value.0: Ah, a worthy opponent! Greetings, I am Stirge the baby-killer, recently escaped from hard time in Waterdeep! My four fellow prisoners and I are now among the most wanted criminals along the Sword Coast.
Why shouldn't I tell you? It's important that you realize I'm not some simple farmer bumbling in the boonies! I am Stirge the baby killer! A powerful cleric of Bhaal, the great lord of murder!

You are correct, my friend. But tell me, before you decide to fight me, isn't there the slightest bit of curiosity in you? Four convicts, locked away in Waterdeep's most inescapable prison... yet here we are!
If you'd listen to what I have to say, I'd be willing to cut my ear from my head and give it to you as proof. Fighting me could prove disastrous to the both of us, most likely you.
If it's all right with you, I'll ask you to leave now. Off you go.
If you'd listen to what I have to say, I'd be willing to cut my ear from my head and give it to you as proof. Of course, you may instead try to kill me but I think you would be quite outmatched.
